'''epe''' is a [[Quenya]] preposition meaning "before".<ref>{{VT|49a}}, p. 12</ref>

The [[Eldar]] imagined future time (time that comes "after" the present) as being "before" them, hence the preposition that means "before" of spatial relationships means "after" when applied to time. 

==Examples==
*''[[epesse|'''epe'''sse]]'' = "after-name"
*''[[epetai|'''epe'''tai]]'' = "consequently"
